Package: MBDDiff
Type: Package
Title: MBDDiff for processing MBDcap-seq datasets
Version: 0.99.0
Date: 2015-11-09
Author: Yuanhang Liu
Maintainer: Yuanhang Liu <liuy12@uthscsa.edu>
Description: Here we presented a novel algorithm, termed MBDDiff, implemented as an R package that is designed specifically for processing MBDCap-seq datasets. MBDDiff contains three modules: quality assessment of datasets and quantification of DNA methylation; determination of differential methylation of promoter regions; and visualization functionalities.
License: GPL (>=3)
Imports: dplyr, RMySQL, doParallel, data.table, pracma, rgl, XBSeq
Depends: R (>= 3.2.0)
Suggests: knitr, rmarkdown, BiocStyle, testthat
VignetteBuilder: knitr
biocViews: DNAMethylation, CpGIsland, QualityControl, Sequencing, Software, Visualization, ExperimentalDesign

